n and a happy new year!<\/li>\n<li>Just here with a holiday message for all: may the season be merry and your homes be bright with fun festivities.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/holiday-greetings-messages-email-header-happy-holidays-simple.png\" alt=\"holiday greetings and messages - happy holidays email header\" width=\"600\" height=\"200\" class=\"wp-image-67920 size-full aligncenter\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/holiday-greetings-messages-email-header-happy-holidays-simple.png 600w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/holiday-greetings-messages-email-header-happy-holidays-simple-480x160.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 600px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\ud83c\udf81 <strong>Use the right messaging to transform your holiday greeting into the gift that keeps on giving<\/strong> with our free guide on <a href=\"https:\/\/marketing.wordstream.com\/WSLIQContentDLWebsite120WordsforMarketingWithEmotion.html?cid=Web_Any_BlogInContent_PPC_120WordsPhrases_Download\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">the 135 best words &amp; phrases for marketing with emotion<\/a>.<\/p>\n<div id=\"short-christmas-wishes\"><\/div>\n<h2>Short Christmas wishes and messages<\/h2>\n<p>These short, merry Christmas wishes and messages can be a nice addition to your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/12\/01\/holiday-email-templates\">email<\/a> signatures, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2021\/12\/03\/christmas-instagram-captions\">holiday Instagram captions<\/a>, and other holiday greetings.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Yes, it\u2019s been said, many times, many ways, but we still mean it just as much! Merry Christmas!<\/li>\n<li>A silent night, a star above, a blessed gift of hope and love. Merry Christmas\ud83c\udf84<\/li>\n<li>Wishing you all the blessings and joys of Christmas and a bright year ahead.<\/li>\n<li>Peace, youth, and happiness for you this Christmas and every other!<\/li>\n<li>Wishing you a fabulous Christmas filled with good cheer, good beer, and memories of a wonderful year.<\/li>\n<li>A little more sparkle, a little less stress, may that be your motto this Christmas!<\/li>\n<li>Good tidings to you, wherever you are, this season!<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"inspirational-christmas-messages\"><\/div>\n<h2>Inspirational Christmas messages<\/h2>\n<p>If you&#8217;re feeling more of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2021\/06\/09\/company-core-values\">core values<\/a> vibe, try working these inspirational Christmas messages into your holiday greetings.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>This Christmas, may your blessings be many, your worries few, and days spent with those who mean the most to you.<\/li>\n<li>The best Christmas gifts are the ones we\u2019ve had all year: a roof over our heads, food in the fridge, and family to enjoy it with. May the richness of gratitude be yours this Christmas!<\/li>\n<li>\ud83c\udf85 Merry Christmas! Enjoy the presents under the tree, the people who put them there, and the extra spark of gratitude the season brings.<\/li>\n<li>Christmas is a time to believe in something greater than yourself\u2014even for just one night.<\/li>\n<li>May the peace and joy of Christmas live in your heart all year long.<\/li>\n<li>\u201cChristmas is forever\u2014not just for one day. For loving, sharing, and giving are not to put away.\u201d \u2013 Norman Wesley Brooks<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/holiday-greetings-messages-email-header-happy-holidays-crew.png\" alt=\"holiday greetings and messages - happy holidays email header\" width=\"600\" height=\"200\" class=\"size-full wp-image-67919 aligncenter\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/holiday-greetings-messages-email-header-happy-holidays-crew.png 600